replies.body:
Ugh, aren't freezes the worst? They ruin a lot of my games too. {{item:3070}} {{item:3070}}

Might be able to figure out what's causing the freezes though! Instead of a driver issue, freezes tend to be a connection issue. Even if other programs like Discord are running, something could be interfering with LoL's connection specifically.
I suggest troubleshooting the game's connection with [**these steps here**](http://riot.com/12B7oac); there are a lot, but following through with each step will help solidify your connection or eliminate it as a potential cause. Get back to me on the results and whether it helped out, and we can work from there!
{{sticker:slayer-pantheon-thumbs}}
